                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221204-147-off760 t18221204-147-crimeloc763"></join>, by the Haberdashers' Arms, on Saturday, the 1st of December, I left a plane there worth 4 s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18221204-147-person1292">
